呢？假設樓價600萬元，承造八成按揭，還款期30年，現時按息約為2.15厘，即每月供款18,104元；若本港加息兩厘，令按息升至4.15厘，屆時每月供款將大增29%至23,333元；的確不是細數目。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T09:10:49.000Z","msg":"唔係細，但都唔大"},{"pid":"4bf385fbfd9b9a1ca9380c6ff73c487436be2194","tid":595894,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T09:22:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99bf7a3c1f43fda2fb8780f0337457acd9104414","tid":595894,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc43a75763ead765bde61366006d984ad511126f","tid":595894,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b19f698f4f7c3c8c33ac09c5cfa2d8405bd79e1","tid":595894,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc541a3e092550a30fd8e99d49df9c55d6758f81","tid":595894,"uid":68556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T08:03:14.000Z","msg":"加到3厘就已經&quot;衝擊&quot;，有無咁弱。  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T08:46:11.000Z","msg":"唔係淨係樓市 商家借錢成本高 匯豐出名會點 你明啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T08:48:58.000Z","msg":"借500萬加3厘好少姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T09:25:43.000Z","msg":"Cut 香港人材啊傻b"},{"pid":"a8c1eb31113730b49afcbbc58d772af743624bff","tid":595894,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8845886359c072b5382cae8c226c7ab9b19b7b0","tid":595894,"uid":13724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1b19f698f4f7c3c8c33ac09c5cfa2d8405bd79e1","tid":595894,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc541a3e092550a30fd8e99d49df9c55d6758f81","tid":595894,"uid":68556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T08:03:14.000Z","msg":"加到3厘就已經&quot;衝擊&quot;，有無咁弱。  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/